Temperature Monitoring
Device
First Product by TECHSPHERE TECHNOLOGIES
Sale Price = Rs. 1500 only
About the product
• The Temperature Monitoring Device comes with 2 main components:
Temperature Monitoring module and Battery Pack.
• Temperature monitoring module has a 7 segment display, buzzer,
Temperature Sensor with 1m long wire and buttons to set temperature and
it is in a 3-D printed case.
• Battery pack comes with 12v battery and bypass charging module and it is
also in a 3-D printed case.
Working Of the Product
• The sensor of the product should be placed inside the refrigerator and then
temperature on which the item should be stored is to be set using the
buttons on the device which is placed outside the refrigerator with the
battery pack.
• When the temperature increases and crosses the temperature set on the
device then the buzzer beeps and alerts the customer about the change.
• It also displays the current temperature inside the refrigerator.
• This device also works when there is a power cut because when the plug is
connected then the module works with the electricity came from the plug
meanwhile the battery also gets charged and during circumstances like
power cut the battery provides the power to the module.
Benefits Of The Product
• This product is useful for doctors, ice cream vendors, pharmacists, etc.
• It can save vaccines worth lakhs of rupees from getting ruined.
• Can save ice creams and prevent the monetary loss of ice cream vendors.
• Can work without electricity.
• Hardly needs any maintenance.
